column1: # Figures on the sheet for 1900 and 1902 are calculated from Boston and Spilsby sites, and have been omitted.
# The exact gauge location is not clear. Somewhere central, but inland, based on the church directions and subsequent move directions.
# The indicative grid reference given is for Lumley Road.
# The gauge arrived from Roman Bank in October 1890 and moved to Marine Gardens in 1904.
